Package: electioncalc
Title: Functions to calculate seats allocation in legislative elections
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Juan José", "García", , "github.icon354@aleeas.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to facilitate the calculation of seat allocation for each political party in a legislative election. Currently, it only includes the D'Hondt method, but it will soon incorporate other well-known methods such as Sainte-Laguë, Imperiali, and others.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
